{"tid":2074234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：請放心，一宗國安案件有10名法官審！","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T07:06:36.000Z","uid":7542,"like":9,"dislike":224,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ca4f1f51c523cf2a985344a12d14b9e06e57e1","tid":2074234,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>真係笑大人個口，由初審計到去終審，有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">11</span></strong></span>個法官？聽到都覺得安心又公平 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「港區國安法草案」說明，特首應從現任或合資格的前任裁判官、法官中指定若干名法官，審理危害國家安全的案件。行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊在本台節目《千禧年代》說，相信不會只指定一、兩位法官，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為要處理初審、上訴到終審的程序，為數不會少於10名法官。</span></strong>不存在特首要求某一法官審理，並判處有罪為止的情況，認為有關推測並無事實根據。他建議，應按照一貫做法，由首席法官指派或指定某法官處理涉及國家安全案件，相信特首一定會聽取司法界的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533376-20200622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533376-20200622.htm&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0Fy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=aa049718\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533376-20200622.htm&h=4cfb0de1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533376-20200622.htm</a>"},{"pid":"76acbf2e01659302a1d90347e1ea841e87cb3fc7","tid":2074234,"uid":997,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"全部都係狗官/支那官"},{"pid":"3d57d5a9c383e9d37dd76af6916b6a5bd5889663","tid":2074234,"uid":7542,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:09:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港法庭就係咁，請面對現實</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBufF8VPWDZg&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0Fy%2B